[06/06/2018 11:19:37] <font color="#ffffff">¿Tú crees?</font>
[06/06/2018 11:19:37] <font color="#ffffff">Yo creo.</font>
[06/06/2018 11:19:41] <font color="#ffffff">(Ruido metálico)</font>
